        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/nintendo-switch-2-unveiling-availability-details-release-date.png" alt="The official unveiling and availability details of the Nintendo Switch 2" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
         <mj-text padding="0px 12px 4px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i>The official unveiling and availability details of the Nintendo Switch 2. Credits: Nintendo/Engadget
</i></p>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              border-left: 3px solid #4D3060;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
                    "><strong>Nintendo will launch the Switch 2 on June 5 for $449.99</strong>. It features a bigger screen, improved storage (256GB), and a magnetic joy controller. Switch 2 introduces features like GameChat, which allows you to make voice and video chats and share screens. Analysts predict strong demand, given the original Switch’s success with over 150 million units sold. Announced games include Mario Kart World and Donkey Kong Bananza (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-03-04-2025-br6-12-official-announcement?source=website" target="_blank">official announcement</a>).</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              border-left: 3px solid #4D3060;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
                    "><strong>A Stanford-led study found that older adults in Wales who received the zoster vaccine were 20% less likely to develop dementia</strong> over seven years. These zoster vaccines attack the neurotropic herpesviruses, which play a role in the pathogenesis of dementia. The findings also revealed that the protective effect was stronger on women than men. (<a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-03-04-2025-br7-13-natures-article?source=website" target="_blank">Nature’s article</a>).</p>

                    <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              border-left: 3px solid #4D3060;
              padding-left: 14px;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
